prompts.frontCover:
A watercolor greeting card front cover for "Lao Lao" from "Jordan". In the center, the text "Happy Birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The scene features two cartoon characters. Person 1, Lao Lao, an East Asian woman in her early 20s with long dark straight hair, a side part, and thin-rimmed glasses, is depicted as a queen sitting on an ornate golden throne. She is wearing a royal gown but keeps her happy smiling expression from the reference photo. She is playfully bonking Person 2 on the head with a scepter. Person 2, Jordan, a Southeast/East Asian man in his early 20s with short, slightly messy black hair, is kneeling beside the throne. He is wearing a colorful jester's hat and outfit, maintaining his joyful, big, broad smile from the reference photo. A banner floats above the throne with the words "Another Year of Ruling". The entire illustration is in a funny, lighthearted watercolor style with soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds. Flat 2D artwork for printing. --ar 5:7 --style raw --v 6.0 --s 150 --c 5

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
